• Deployment: Wisecow app hosted on an AWS Lightsail instance with a single-node K3s cluster.

• Automation: On each push, a new Docker image is built and deployed to the cluster.

• Process: New pods are created with the updated image, and old pods are deleted.

• Time Taken: Completed the setup in approximately 10 hours.

• URL: wisecow.pranavparihar.site

